query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(t ci) NoHashJoin(ci it1 it2 mi mi_idx t n) */ select min(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
min(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from title AS t
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1999 AND 2004 AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(writer)',
'(producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '6.1'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.note IS NULL AND mi.info IN ('Action',
'War')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres'
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender IS NOT NULL AND n.gender = 'm';
